Changelog
=========

1.2.2 (unreleased)
------------------

- No changes yet.


1.2.1 (2013-05-01)
------------------

- Removed a superfluous np-modindex link that was being added to the navigation
  in all HTML documentation.  It seems to come from numpydoc, and is specific
  to generating a module index for Numpy modules.

- Moved the sidebar in the Sphinx HTML template from the right side of the page
  to the left.

- Updated the intersphinx URL for matplotlib.

- Use the enumitem LaTeX package to support additional levels of item nesting.


1.1 (2011-08-31)
----------------

- Initial public release.
